dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Valdepenas, sheet 62. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 39.0000. South Decimal Degree 38.0000. East Decimal Degree -3.0000. West Decimal Degree -4.0000. Alternate title: Valdepe~nas, Spain. Polyconic projection. With Spanish-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Spain, 1:50,000, Instituto Geografico, 1887-1935; Spain, 1:200,000, Cuartel General del Generalisimo, Sheets 65 and 75, 1939; Road Map of Spain and Portugal, 1:400,000, A.M.S., Sheets 47 and 49, Third Edition, 1943; Railways of Spain and Portugal 1:1,500,000, G.S.G.S., 1942. Corrected from Intelligence Reports, 1942 and 1943. Partially revised from aerial photography, 1943.".
